sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant K as Keycloak
  participant G as Istio Gateway
  participant Q as Kuadrant
  participant B as Backend
  U->>G: GET /api/customers
  G->>Q: Validate JWT
  Q-->>U: 302 Login if no token
  U->>K: Login + credentials
  K-->>U: Token
  U->>G: GET /api with Bearer token
  G->>Q: Validate JWT OK
  Note over G,Q: Rate limit per user
  G->>B: Forward
  B-->>U: 200 OK data
